        <p>
          The witch trials created victims whose deaths were acknowledged as wrongful within a generation of their execution. This official recognition‚Äîrare in cases of historical injustice‚Äîmay contribute to Salem's haunted reputation. The executed weren't criminals; they were innocent people killed by their neighbors.
        </p>
        <p>
